{
  "stem": "11075.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was walking in the street, and they said-- but everybody told me that I don't look like a Jew.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was afraid to open my mouth, because the Polish people are anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One thing, they know it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Germans, they couldn't recognize are you a Jew, or you're a German, or you are English, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- the Polack, he pointed with the finger, Jew, Jew, Jew, Jew, Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And right away, they took, you know, to the cemetery over there, where we used to be there, in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from Plaszow, they built anti-Semite, anti-Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They built, you know, barracks for us to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The liquidation in Plaszow, you know, I mean the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then we went, you know, to-- to-- to a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Krakow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went straight-- I didn't know what to do, so I went straight to-- to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the ghetto, I met already my cousin, Banchur, who was the factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Schindler came in a couple of times, Oskar Schindler, because he got already the key.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, you know, even the liquidation from Krakow or ghetto will be-- will-- the liquidation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you will go, you know, to Jerozolimska, where the cemetery is, and you will stay over there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But from over there, they will make a list.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They will make a list how many people will go to the factory working.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they will sleep over there by Oskar Schindler.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was lucky that they're still in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- so my cousin Banchur asked Schindler, and he said-- because that was his factory-- make sure that Henry Weil is on the list.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because Banchur, in the factory, when we were working, you know, by Oskar Schindler, he helped me a lot.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
